title: Jinlilu - Chunghwayori
description: Chinese vegetarian restaurant near Hoegi Station, exit 2. To get there, go out Hoegi Station exit 2 and turn right, walk down alley past the bedding shop and turn left, the restaurant is across the street from the wedding hall, in an alley behind a bank, it's on the second floor, sign says 중화요리 and has pictures of mushrooms on it. Serves mainstays of Koreanized Chinese food including jjambbong, jjajangmyeon, palbochae, and so on. Uses mushrooms rather than processed fake meats.
